OL,4,G1210FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe B&Bers are still in Cornwall
OL,6,     Gfor the week's second visit, at
OL,7,     GThe Llawnroc Hotel, where former
OL,8,     GRedcoats Craig and Rachel are
OL,9,     Gbanking on being able to keep
OL,10,     Gtheir guests entertained.
OL,11,G1240FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GIt's a hat-trick! The B&Bers
OL,13,     Gspend a third consecutive visit
OL,14,     Gin Cornwall, at ex-military man
OL,15,     GJo's The Olde Malthouse, where
OL,16,     Ghe's hoping to wow his guests
OL,17,     Gwith his B&B's heritage charm.
