OL,4,G1315FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe B&Bers head to Dorset for the
OL,6,     Gweek's final visit, at The
OL,7,     GBritannia Inn, run by Hannah and
OL,8,     GLee. The controversial pricing at
OL,9,     Gbreakfast leaves one guest with a
OL,10,     Gsour taste.
OL,11,G1345FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GIt's payment day, and time to
OL,13,     Gfind out who's won. It's been a
OL,14,     Gweek of vitriol, with lots of
OL,15,     GB&Bers choosing not to return to
OL,16,     Gthe others' establishments. Will
OL,17,     Git all kick off? Probably.
